Nó đi rồi, phải không?

353
00:33:52,760 --> 00:33:54,750
Danny, chơi tiếp mau.

354
00:34:06,730 --> 00:34:09,500
- Danny, đưa lá bài đây.
- Nó vẫn đang chạy.

355
00:34:12,740 --> 00:34:14,710
Nhanh lên.

356
00:34:16,380 --> 00:34:17,900
Lá bài.

357
00:34:37,700 --> 00:34:40,030
Lá bài nói gì vậy?

358
00:35:26,410 --> 00:35:27,780
Danny!

359
00:35:53,240 --> 00:35:54,470
Danny!

360
00:35:55,240 --> 00:35:57,100
Anh Walter!

361
00:36:47,020 --> 00:36:48,720
Gì vậy?

362
00:36:53,730 --> 00:36:55,990
- Chuyện gì vậy?
